Algodex is a highly decentralized marketplace with the order book completely on the Algorand blockchain itself. The expected release date is Q4 2021 however, it may be delayed due to security auditors being extremely busy.
Algodex supports limit orders so you can rest assured your trade will only occur at the price you set. All assets on the Algorand blockchain are supported in Algodex by default. If it exists, you can trade it.

